premise_source_doc_sentence: Nine men have achieved the 100 metres and 200 metres ` Double ' at the same Olympic Games - Archie Hahn  (  1904  )  , Ralph Craig  (  1912  )  , Percy Williams  (  1928  )  , Eddie Tolan  (  1932  )  , Jesse Owens  (  1936  )  , Bobby Morrow  (  1956  )  , Valeriy Borzov  (  1972  )  , Carl Lewis  (  1984  )  , and Usain Bolt  (  2008 , 2012 , 2016  )  .
